textline.data: Requirement description:
The system shall use an object detection sensor
Requirement description:
The system shall dispence the selected drink to a user
Requirement description:
The system shall calculate the sufficient funds
depending on the presence of a mug
Requirement description:
The system shall detect the presence of a mug
Requirement description: Alarm
When the application is finished, the system shall
notify the user with a beep sound
Requirement description:
When the application starts, if the wallet contains the sufficient funds, the
machine shall dispence the selected drink within 5 or 6 senconds
Requirement description: Drink type
The system shall dispence either coffee or tea
Requirement description: Coin acceptance
The system shall only accept 50 cent coins
Requirement description: Drink Selection
The system shall manage the user selection of the drink
